description: An old Belgian family recipe is taking your taste buds to all new heights of excitement, thanks to Bruges Waffle Bus.Authentic, fresh, and always delicious, Salt Lake City's most superb waffles are made perfect for you each and every time. If you've never had a caramelized waffle before, then Bruges Waffle Bus is a truck you can't miss.Make your day amazing with the classic Belgian flavor you'll only find on this food truck!
name: Bruges Waffle Bus
